I Have been trying to use up stuff (Meats) in my freezer . Today I found lamb neck bones,&nbsp; trimmings from the Christmas&nbsp; smoked prime rib. and a pound of stew beef. Cooking all that up in the dutch oven to make the stew starter.
I have red Yukon potatoes , carrots, onions, and corn to put in the stew.&nbsp; 
Hope it turns out.
